{"tid":950802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[八達通…]台灣高雄捷運正式支援綁定 MasterCard 手機入閘","createTime":"2018-12-21T20:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T03:20:28.000Z","uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33c6470c58d087abeaa7fd6a00c6b382e9dcaca4","tid":950802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T20:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Du2r7vPVsAEvecw-770x439_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2FDu2r7vPVsAEvecw-770x439_c.jpg&h=117d438b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據台灣《蘋果仁》報道，有台灣網友在 Twitter 上表示高雄捷運已經開始支援以綁定 MasterCard 的手機來入閘，只要手機綁定 MasterCard ，無論 Apple Pay 、 Google Pay 或 Samsung Pay 都可以入閘。<br />\n<br />\n報道指這是繼倫敦地鐵和新加坡地鐵後，全球第三個引入 MasterCard 支付的公共運輸工具。目前高雄捷運鹽埕站已經換上了MasterCard 感應設備，而除了上述三種手機支付方式之外，也同時支援台灣 Pay 、中國銀聯 Union Pay 和 MasterCard 直接感應入閘。不過現時台北捷運就未知何時開始支援。<br />\n<br />\n另外，也還未可以設定成 Apple Pay 的特快交通卡。特快交通卡是指可以不用 Touch ID 或 FaceID 認證就可以入閘，加快入閘速度。此外，特快交通卡可以在手機沒電的情況下使用。日本的 Suica 卡、北京一卡通和上海交通卡都支援設定成 Apple Pay 的特快交通卡。<br />\n<br />\n星期三網上曾經有傳聞指香港八達通將支援 Apple Pay ，令一眾果粉為之雀躍。不過在當日的八達通記者會中僅公布讓 iPhone 和沒有 NFC 的 Android 手機可以查閱八達通紀錄。現時香港僅可以透過 Samsung Pay 手機支付入閘，而使用 QR Code 支付的入閘方式就要等到 2020 年，遠遠落後於隣近地區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/12/21/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E6%8D%B7%E9%81%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E7%B6%81%E5%AE%9Amastercard%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F12%2F21%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%258D%25B7%25E9%2581%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E7%25B6%2581%25E5%25AE%259Amastercard%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2596%2598%2F&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=de70bd08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/12/21/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E6%8D%B7%E9%81%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E7%B6%81%E5%AE%9Amastercard%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%96%98/</a>"},{"pid":"12baa0ea0ebd056daa4366140c45d38a15eca602","tid":950802,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T20:49:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵我屌你老母個臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb1dcf65eb164224a52c0d331923d4c9f5e3b29","tid":950802,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:52:18.000Z","msg":"八達通股東係?  股東既股東係...?"},{"pid":"dddb9c64829d2294751be1a95ce2a10219d21e4b","tid":950802,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:56:56.000Z","msg":"八達通有政府做後台，班管理層返朝九晚五，返到去R屎忽收人工又一date，驚閪"},{"pid":"994a8af8a1c80480b51a8df5a282b682851c7a13","tid":950802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"香港收card好似要2022年先得<br />\n點解要咁撚耐 真心唔明"},{"pid":"8608751ad4c515c002222d91cb9797ef5b56a88c","tid":950802,"uid":158977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"994a8af8a1c80480b51a8df5a282b682851c7a13","tid":950802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"香港收card好似要2022年先得<br />\n點解要咁撚耐 真心唔明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"因為而家仲考緊古 整qr曲方便支那人用<br />\n屌你老母港鐵仲話加價 食屎啦"},{"pid":"310e4592fdd2d92398b197e3e7323a682875c596","tid":950802,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"香港如果失去國際地位都係因為班老屎忽"},{"pid":"9bafa25dcccac308bcca6365b8884947e99f8109","tid":950802,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cca4f0e0e770bd547c79280e051f09fd0d518336","tid":950802,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8608751ad4c515c002222d91cb9797ef5b56a88c","tid":950802,"uid":158977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"994a8af8a1c80480b51a8df5a282b682851c7a13","tid":950802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"